<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/favicon.png">
    <meta name="description"
        content="Follow our whole-house deep clean checklist to transform your home in a weekend. Detailed room-by-room tasks to ensure every corner is spotless and refreshed.">
    <title>Deep Clean Checklist - Home Hub</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com/3.4.16"></script>
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        primary: "#14B8A6",
                        secondary: "#0F766E",
                    },
                    borderRadius: {
                        none: "0px",
                        sm: "4px",
                        DEFAULT: "8px",
                        md: "12px",
                        lg: "16px",
                        xl: "20px",
                        "2xl": "24px",
                        "3xl": "32px",
                        full: "9999px",
                        button: "8px",
                    },
                },
            },
        };
    </script>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Pacifico&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/remixicon/4.6.0/remixicon.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/responsive.css">
</head>

<body class="bg-white">
    <%- include("../partials/header") %>

        <main class="py-8 bg-white">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                    <article class="lg:col-span-2">
                        <div class="bg-white">
                            <nav class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">
                                <a href="/" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Home</a>
                                <span class="mx-2">></span>
                                <a href="/cleaning" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Cleaning</a>
                                <span class="mx-2">></span>
                                <span class="text-gray-800">Deep Clean Checklist</span>
                            </nav>

                            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 leading-tight">
                                Whole-House Deep Clean Checklist for a Weekend
                            </h1>

                            <div class="mb-8">
                                <img src="/images/deep-clean-checklist.webp" alt="Checklist for deep cleaning a house"
                                    class="w-full h-80 object-cover rounded-lg shadow-lg" fetchpriority="high">
                            </div>

                            <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
                                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Introduction</h2>
                                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                                    Sometimes your home needs more than just a quick tidy. A deep clean resets your
                                    environment and identifies maintenance issues before they become problems. This
                                    checklist breaks down the tasks by room to make the job manageable.
                                </p>

                                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Kitchen Deep Clean</h2>
                                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
                                    <li><strong>Appliances:</strong> Clean inside the oven, microwave, and refrigerator.
                                    </li>
                                    <li><strong>Cabinets:</strong> Wipe down the fronts and vacuum inside the drawers.
                                    </li>
                                    <li><strong>Dishwasher:</strong> Run a cleaning cycle with vinegar or a specialized
                                        cleaner.</li>
                                    <li><strong>Walls and Backsplash:</strong> Remove grease splatters and dust.</li>
                                </ul>

                                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Living and Bedrooms</h2>
                                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
                                    <li><strong>Dusting:</strong> Reach high ceiling fans, crown molding, and
                                        baseboards.</li>
                                    <li><strong>Windows:</strong> Wash glass and clean out the tracks.</li>
                                    <li><strong>Upholstery:</strong> Vacuum under couch cushions and steam clean if
                                        possible.</li>
                                    <li><strong>Linens:</strong> Wash all bedding, including pillows and mattress
                                        protectors.</li>
                                </ul>

                                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Conclusion</h2>
                                <p class="text-gray-700">
                                    Tackling one room at a time will keep you motivated. Once finished, you'll feel an
                                    immediate difference in the air quality and atmosphere of your home.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </article>

                    <aside class="lg:col-span-1">
                        <div class="sticky top-8 space-y-6">
                            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
                                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Pro Tool Tip</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-600">Invest in micro-fiber cloths for dusting. They trap particles
                                    rather than just moving them around, speeding up your deep clean significantly.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </aside>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>

        <%- include("../partials/footer") %>
            <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>

</html>